@startuml
actor User
participant API
participant Database

User -> API : POST /api/candidates/
API -> Database : Save candidate details
Database --> API : Confirmation
API --> User : Response with candidate ID

User -> API : GET /api/candidates/
API -> Database : Fetch all candidates
Database --> API : List of candidates
API --> User : JSON response

User -> API : GET /api/recruiters/
API -> Database : Fetch all recruiters
Database --> API : List of recruiters
API --> User : JSON response
@enduml

